00:25:41.416 --> 00:25:42.936 A:middle
in my game world's terms.

00:25:43.876 --> 00:25:45.836 A:middle
GKGraphNode is also
useful when you want

00:25:45.836 --> 00:25:48.306 A:middle
to manually make your own
