00:27:14.056 --> 00:27:14.726 A:middle
that we just talked about,

00:27:14.726 --> 00:27:17.256 A:middle
to automatically generate
an obstacle from that node,

00:27:17.966 --> 00:27:19.776 A:middle
update the underlying
