00:42:42.286 --> 00:42:43.896 A:middle
And you can see how easy it is

00:42:44.216 --> 00:42:45.896 A:middle
to make random sources
a part of your game.

00:42:46.336 --> 00:42:48.306 A:middle
It's only a couple lines of
