00:50:01.626 --> 00:50:03.496 A:middle
The grade of a fact is the
system's confidence in it,

00:50:04.016 --> 00:50:06.216 A:middle
and this allows us
to use fuzzy logic

00:50:06.216 --> 00:50:07.896 A:middle
